history.text: Hello, how are you?  I'd like to tell you about a fabulous movie directed by Christopher Nolan called "Inception".
Hi, I'm fine thanks.  Tell me all about it!

This movie was released in 2009 and stars Leonardo DiCaprio, Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Ellen Page, and Tom Hardy.  It's a story about "extractors", who try to infiltrate the subconscious of certain victims in order to get information from them.  This is the so called "inception"
Sounds like science fiction, kind of.  I am a big fan of the cast, honestly, and it sounds very interesting.  Has it gotten good reviews?

While it's traditionally considered a sci fi movie, it has elements of a love story that can intrigue those who aren't huge sci fi fans, so perhaps that would interest you as well.  It's really a complex and unique plot that is sure to intrigue the viewer
Yes, the reviews were fantastic!  IT has 86% on rotten tomatoes
It sounds fantastic.  I would definitely be interested in seeing this movie.
as well as scoring 8.8/10 on imdb, which is rpety impressive because those people are pretty harsh
